Package: SamSeq
Type: Package
Title: Work with aligned reads from a SAM file
Version: 0.0.1
Author: Stuart R. Jefferys
Maintainer: Stuart R. Jefferys <srj@unc.edu>
Description: Work with the aligned read data as provided in a *.sam file, as in
 the format used by SamTools. Tracks header information, reads, and the source
 file. Loads all reads and optionally the extra read tags. Includes functions to
 translate the Sam flags and to filter reads.
